Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:17.75,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Olá!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:20.74,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Bom dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.58,0:00:54.69,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Se eu puder ser que nem a {\i0}idol{\i1} Miki-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.23,0:00:58.50,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,e ser legal e me dar bem,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.71,0:01:00.85,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,então eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:03.40,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,na minha nova escola...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:09.50,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,poderei fazer várias...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:10.58,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,várias...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.44,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,várias...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:18.27,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,amigas!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:21.58,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Eba!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:22.73,italics,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Consegui!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:28.44,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.03,0:01:30.26,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Que gelada...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.26,0:01:32.63,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,Estava me perguntando\Nquem havia caído na água.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:35.81,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Taira-san, boa tarde!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.81,0:01:37.08,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,Sabia que era você, Komichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:39.61,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, isso aqui foi porque...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.61,0:01:42.21,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,eu tava nadando de roupa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:46.15,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,Te dou uma carona até sua casa.\NSobe na traseira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:51.61,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,Soube que passou no vestibulinho\Npra escola que escolheu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:53.55,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Sim, a Academia Roubai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:55.60,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,É uma escola particular!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:59.36,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,Essa escola parece ser dureza.\NA sua mãe não estudou lá?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.36,0:02:03.08,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Sim. Por isso tô tão feliz\Nde ter entrado!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.08,0:02:04.82,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, é mesmo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:08.28,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Dizem que as turmas têm mais\Nque dez alunas cada!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:10.42,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Nem consigo imaginar como é isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:12.70,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,Bom, na Escola Primária Futaba,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:14.90,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,você era a única na turma, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:16.94,main,Taira,0000,0000,0000,,Fico feliz por você!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:19.74,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,É!
