Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:39.33,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cheguei.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.71,0:02:42.13,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Mãe, a onee-chan chegou!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:44.97,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.57,0:02:48.23,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Não achou os passos dela\Nmeio suspeitos, não?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:49.96,main,Kao,0000,0000,0000,,Vou lá ver!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.56,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Você é uma moleca, mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:56.51,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,A quem será que puxou, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:02:58.28,main,Yuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, é mesmo.
